'''阴茎骨'''是一根在多种[[哺乳动物|有胎盘哺乳动物]]的[[阴茎|阴茎]]中存在的[[骨|骨头]]，在[[阴茎|人类阴茎]]中不存在，而存在于其他多种[[灵长目|灵长目动物]]（如[[大猩猩|大猩猩]]和[[黑猩猩|黑猩猩]]）的阴茎中<ref name="patterns"/>。阴茎骨位于雄性[[尿道|尿道]]上方，有助于在[[性交|性行为]]中插入时保持足够的硬度，雌性起相同作用的是'''阴蒂骨'''——一根在[[阴蒂|阴蒂]]里的[[骨|骨头]]<ref>{{cite book |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=MFw4AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA264&lpg=PA264#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Biological Actions of Sex Hormones |page=264 |author=Harold Burrows |publisher=Cambridge University Press |year=1945 |accessdate=4 August 2012 |archive-date=2014-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104151636/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=MFw4AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA264&lpg=PA264#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Ewer1973-2">{{cite book|author=R. F. Ewer|title=The Carnivores|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=IETMd3-lSlkC&printsec=frontcover#v=snippet&q=os%20clitoridis&f=false|accessdate=16 December 2012|year=1973|publisher=Cornell University Press|isbn=978-0-8014-8493-3|archive-date=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707080020/http://books.google.com/books?id=IETMd3-lSlkC&printsec=frontcover#v=snippet&q=os%20clitoridis&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 作用 ==
阴茎骨主要用于[[交配|交配]]，不同[[物种|物种]]的阴茎骨大小形状往往不同，甚至两个相似物种的阴茎骨特征也往往相异。阴茎中的骨头使得雄性可以长时间的与雌性交配<ref>Dixson, A. F. "Baculum length and copulatory behaviour in carnivores and pinnipeds (Grand Order Ferae)." Journal of Zoology 235.1 (1995): 67-76.</ref>，在繁殖策略中这是一个很明显的优势<ref name="WWB"/>。

== 在哺乳动物中 ==
[[Image:Raccoonpenisbone.jpg|thumb]]
多种[[真兽下纲|真兽下纲]]的[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]有阴茎骨（雄性）和阴蒂骨（雌性）：
*[[灵长目|灵长目]]，不包括[[人类|人类]]和[[蜘蛛猴|蜘蛛猴]]。
*[[啮齿目|啮齿目]]（啮齿动物）<ref name="HarknessTurner2013">{{cite book|first1=John E.|last1=Harkness|first2=Patricia V.|last2=Turner|first3=Susan|last3=VandeWoude|first4=Colette L.|last4=Wheler|title=Harkness and Wagner's Biology and Medicine of Rabbits and Rodents|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=GJIOPzAVNCoC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=penis&f=false|date=2 April 2013|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-1-118-70907-8|access-date=2014-10-30|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628030421/http://books.google.com/books?id=GJIOPzAVNCoC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=penis&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但不存在于近亲[[兔形目|兔形目]]（如家兔、野兔等）中。
*[[食虫目|食虫目]]（食虫动物），包括[[鼹鼠|鼹鼠]]、[[鼱鼩|鼱鼩]]和[[刺猬|刺猬]]等。
*[[食肉目|食肉目]]<ref name="Ewer1973">{{cite book|author=R. F. Ewer|title=The Carnivores|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=IETMd3-lSlkC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=baculum&f=false|accessdate=16 December 2012|year=1973|publisher=Cornell University Press|isbn=978-0-8014-8493-3|archive-date=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707080020/http://books.google.com/books?id=IETMd3-lSlkC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=baculum&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括许多广为人知的[[科_(生物)|科]]，如[[熊科|熊科]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Dyck |first1=Markus G. |first2=Jackie M. |last2=Bourgeois |first3=Edward H. |last3=Miller |year=2004 |journal=Journal of Zoology |volume=264 |issue=1 |pages=105–110 |url=http://journals.cambridge.org/action/displayAbstract;jsessionid=3332AADA7ADA71727F83E689232BAB80.tomcat1?fromPage=online&aid=241981 |doi=10.1017/S0952836904005606 |title=Growth and variation in the bacula of polar bears (''Ursus maritimus'') in the Canadian Arctic |access-date=2014-10-30 |archive-date=2014-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031115731/http://journals.cambridge.org/action/displayAbstract;jsessionid=3332AADA7ADA71727F83E689232BAB80.tomcat1?fromPage=online&aid=241981 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[猫科|猫科]]、[[犬科|犬科]]<ref name="EvansLahunta2013">{{cite book|author1=Howard E. Evans|author2=Alexander de Lahunta|title=Miller's Anatomy of the Dog|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=6eBOAQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=%22os%20penis%22&f=false|date=7 August 2013|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=978-0-323-26623-9|access-date=2014-10-30|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628030413/http://books.google.com/books?id=6eBOAQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=%22os%20penis%22&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[鳍足亚目|鳍足亚目]]（[[海象|海象]]、[[海豹|海豹]]、[[海狮|海狮]]）<ref name="PerrinWursig2009">{{cite book|author1=William F. Perrin|author2=Bernd Wursig|author3=J. G.M. Thewissen|title=Encyclopedia of Marine Mammals|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=2rkHQpToi9sC&pg=PA68&dq=pinniped+baculum&hl=en&sa=X&ei=otYCU4rBHKuR1AHXxoDgDg&ved=0CCkQ6AEwAA#v=snippet&q=baculum&f=false|date=26 February 2009|publisher=Academic Press|isbn=978-0-08-091993-5|pages=68–|access-date=2014-10-30|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628030415/http://books.google.com/books?id=2rkHQpToi9sC&pg=PA68&dq=pinniped+baculum&hl=en&sa=X&ei=otYCU4rBHKuR1AHXxoDgDg&ved=0CCkQ6AEwAA#v=snippet&q=baculum&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[浣熊科|浣熊科]]（[[浣熊|浣熊]]等）<ref name="Silvy2012"/>、[[鼬科|鼬科]]（[[水獭|水獭]]、[[黄鼠狼|黄鼠狼]]、[[臭鼬|臭鼬]]和其他）<ref>Baryshnikov, Gennady F., Olaf RP Bininda-Emonds, and Alexei V. Abramov. "Morphological variability and evolution of the baculum (os penis) in Mustelidae (Carnivora)." Journal of Mammalogy 84.2 (2003): 673-690.</ref>。犬型动物的阴茎骨通常比猫型动物的要长<ref name = "Ewer1973" />。
*[[翼手目|翼手目]]，[[蝙蝠|蝙蝠]]等。

阴茎骨不存在于[[人类|人类]]、[[有蹄类|有蹄类哺乳动物]]<ref name="Nowak1999">{{cite book|author=Ronald M. Nowak|title=Walker's Mammals of the World|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=7W-DGRILSBoC&pg=PA1007&dq=ungulate+baculum&hl=en&sa=X&ei=WpnqU_TIH8yMyATL_YKoBw&ved=0CB4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=ungulate%20baculum&f=false|date=7 April 1999|publisher=JHU Press|isbn=978-0-8018-5789-8|pages=1007–|access-date=2014-10-30|archive-date=2015-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151230101337/https://books.google.com/books?id=7W-DGRILSBoC&pg=PA1007&dq=ungulate+baculum&hl=en&sa=X&ei=WpnqU_TIH8yMyATL_YKoBw&ved=0CB4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=ungulate%20baculum&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[象科|象科动物]]、[[单孔目|单孔目动物]]([[鸭嘴兽|鸭嘴兽]]、[[针鼹|针鼹]]）、[[有袋类|有袋类哺乳动物]]<ref name="Szalay2006">{{cite book|author=Frederick S. Szalay|title=Evolutionary History of the Marsupials and an Analysis of Osteological Characters|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=HmQTTChULOMC&pg=PA293&dq=marsupial+baculum&hl=en&sa=X&ei=cZrqU4OgOcSAygSx6oGAAg&ved=0CEIQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=marsupial%20baculum&f=false|date=11 May 2006|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-0-521-02592-8|pages=293–|access-date=2014-10-30|archive-date=2015-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151230101339/https://books.google.com/books?id=HmQTTChULOMC&pg=PA293&dq=marsupial+baculum&hl=en&sa=X&ei=cZrqU4OgOcSAygSx6oGAAg&ved=0CEIQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=marsupial%20baculum&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[兔形目|兔形目动物]]、[[鬣狗科|鬣狗科动物]]<ref name="Estes1991">{{cite book|author=Richard Estes|title=The Behavior Guide to African Mammals: Including Hoofed Mammals, Carnivores, Primates|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=g977LsZHpcsC&pg=PA323&dq=spotted+hyena+penis&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9BHIUM_LM--x0AHJz4CwCA&ved=0CDwQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=boneless&f=false|accessdate=12 December 2012|year=1991|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=978-0-520-08085-0|pages=323–|archive-date=2014-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108021931/http://books.google.com/books?id=g977LsZHpcsC&pg=PA323&dq=spotted+hyena+penis&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9BHIUM_LM--x0AHJz4CwCA&ved=0CDwQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=boneless&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[鲸目|鲸目动物]]（[[鲸|鲸]]、[[海豚|海豚]]和[[鼠海豚|鼠海豚]]）的体内。

在[[哺乳动物|有胎盘哺乳动物]]中如此广泛的存在表明哺乳动物在很早的时候便已经进化出了阴茎骨，而随后又有相当一部分的哺乳动物失去了它。

体重约500克的[[灵长目|灵长目动物]][[狨属|狨属]]长有大约2毫米长的阴茎骨，而一只小至63克的[[婴猴科|婴猴科]]动物却有约13毫米长的阴茎骨。类人猿类动物尽管体型巨大，却倾向于长有较小的阴茎骨，而人类也是它们之中唯一一个失去了阴茎骨的种类。<ref name="WWB"/>

在一些哺乳动物（如浣熊）中，阴茎骨可以用来判断大致年龄，如果阴茎骨的末端的软骨并未钙化、有着多孔的底部、质量小于1.2克且长度不超过90毫米，那么这根阴茎骨属于一只未成年雄性。<ref name="Silvy2012">{{cite book|author=Nova J. Silvy|title=The Wildlife Techniques Manual: Volume 1: Research. Volume 2: Management 2-vol. Set|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=PL2IHTdzSeAC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=raccoon%20baculum&f=false|date=7 February 2012|publisher=JHU Press|isbn=978-1-4214-0159-1|access-date=2014-10-30|archive-date=2014-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140130013142/http://books.google.com/books?id=PL2IHTdzSeAC&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=raccoon%20baculum&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 在人类中的缺席 ==
不像其他灵长目动物，人类没有阴茎骨或阴蒂骨。然而，在[[类人猿|类人猿]]中这根骨头也是退化了的，在很多[[猿|猿类]]中那只是一根相对来说无关紧要的10到20毫米长的东西。有案例报告称某些人的[[阴茎|阴茎]]因创伤而硬化<ref>{{cite journal |last=Sarma |first=Deba |author2=Thomas Weilbaecher |year=1990 |title=Human os penis |journal=Urology |volume=35 |issue= 4|pages=349–350 |doi=10.1016/0090-4295(90)80163-H |pmid=2108520 }}</ref>，还有一个案例称曾在一名五岁男孩的身上手术取出过一根阴茎骨，而这名男孩身上还存在其他进化异常现象，如阴囊裂开<ref>{{cite journal |last=Champion |first=RH |author2=J Wegrzyn |year=1964 |title=Congenital os penis |journal=Journal of Urology |volume=91 |pages=663–4 |pmid=14172255 }}</ref>。{{link-en|Clellan S. Ford|Clellan S. Ford}}和{{link-en|Frank A. Beach|Frank A. Beach}}在1953年出版的《性行为模式》第30页写道：“[[大猩猩|大猩猩]]和[[黑猩猩|黑猩猩]]都拥有一根阴茎骨，后者的阴茎骨在器官的下方部分，大约有3/4英寸长。”<ref name="patterns">''Patterns of Sexual Behavior''  Clellan S. Ford and Frank A. Beach, published by Harper & Row, New York in 1951. ISBN 0-313-22355-6</ref>对人类来说，[[勃起|勃起]]时的硬度则完全由[[海绵体|海绵体]]内的[[血压|血压]]来保持。

据推测，阴茎骨在人类体内消失却存在于我们的近亲[[黑猩猩|黑猩猩]]体内，这是因为人类“演化出一种雄性长时间陪在特定雌性身边来保证自己后代的血缘的繁殖系统”<ref name="WWB">{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/beasts/evidence/prog1/page4_2.htm|title=Godinotia|year=2002|work=Walking With Beasts|publisher=ABC — BBC|pages=Question: How do we know how Godinotia  (the primate in program 1) mated?|accessdate=29 June 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429220805/http://www.abc.net.au/beasts/evidence/prog1/page4_2.htm|archive-date=2014-04-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，这一系统允许短时间内多次交配。观察证实，拥有阴茎骨的灵长目雄性只是频繁的遇到异性，阴茎骨使得进行长时间的交配成为可能，从而最大化他们成为雌性的后代的父亲的可能性。人类女性表现出的“隐蔽排卵”特性使得了解她们什么时候处于可怀孕状态是几乎不可能的，因此频繁性交有助于保证血缘<ref name="WWB"/>。

进化生物学家[[理查德·道金斯|理查德·道金斯]]1989年推测，阴茎骨在人类体内消失却存在于我们的近亲[[黑猩猩|黑猩猩]]体内，是雌性于可能的交配中在身体健康的雄性身上寻找“忠诚信号”的[[性选择|性选择]]的结果<ref>{{cite book| title = Richard Dawkins: How a Scientist Changed the Way We Think : Reflections by Scientists, Writers, and Philosophers| url = http://books.google.com/?id=gPL7LqY8NSsC| year = 2007| publisher = Oxford University Press| isbn = 0-19-921466-2| page = 228| first1 = Mark| last1 = Ridley}}, [http://books.google.com/books?id=gPL7LqY8NSsC&pg=PA228Extract of page 228] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=gPL7LqY8NSsC&pg=PA228Extract |date=20160414092647 }}</ref>。人类[[阴茎|阴茎]]仅仅依赖血压实现勃起使得这对血压变化特别敏感，无法勃起不仅仅归因于身体（如糖尿病或神经系统疾病），也可能因为精神（如压力或紧张）<ref>{{cite book |last=Dawkins |first=Richard |authorlink=Richard Dawkins |title=[[The_Selfish_Gene|The Selfish Gene]] |edition=30th anniversary |year=2006 |publisher= Oxford University Press|location=Endnote to 30th anniversary edition |isbn=0-19-929114-4 |quote=It is not implausible that, with natural selection refining their diagnostic skills, females could glean all sorts of clues about a male’s health, and robustness of his ability to cope with stress, from the tone and bearing of his penis.|page=[https://archive.org/details/selfishgene00dawk_669/page/158 158] endnote |origyear= 1978}}</ref>。

== 文化意义 ==
阴茎骨的存在是不可能逃过游牧和狩猎文化的注意的（见下文）。

戴着浣熊的阴茎骨有时被认为能带来好运或生育。

=== Oosik ===
'''Oosik'''是[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]当地文化中对[[海象|海象]]、[[海豹|海豹]]、[[海狮|海狮]]和[[北极熊|北极熊]]的阴茎骨的称呼。长达60厘米（2英尺）的阴茎骨[[化石|化石]]经常被抛光后作为[[匕首|匕首]]和其它工具的柄，oosik就指的是这些北极食肉动物的阴茎骨打磨和雕刻后的产物。

Oosik还频繁作为纪念品被[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]本地人出售给游客，2007年，一根被出售者认为是现存最大的长达4.5英尺（1.4米）的已灭绝的海象阴茎骨化石卖了8000美元。<ref name="4.5foot">{{cite web |url=http://sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/n/a/2007/08/26/state/n154935D40.DTL |title=Walrus penis sells for $8,000 at Beverly Hills action |accessdate=30 August 2007 |work=AP |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071106050910/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fn%2Fa%2F2007%2F08%2F26%2Fstate%2Fn154935D40.DTL |archivedate=2007-11-06|deadurl=yes }}</ref>

